  "title": "👀 OFFICE LIFE NOT YOUR THING? -- EVENTS AND MARKETING 🏆🎯",
  "description": "<p>If the idea of sitting at a desk all day sounds… meh 💻😵‍💫<br />but you also don’t want something too tiring 😌<br />this might actually suit you.</p><p>At <strong>Thrive Organization</strong>, we work with brands through face-to-face marketing 🤝<br />It’s a full-time role where you interact with people, work with a team, and pick up real skills — without the corporate stiffness.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do 👇</strong><br />• Talk to people & share product info 🗣️<br />• Help out at booths & simple events 🎪<br />• Work with teammates 👊<br />• Build communication & confidence 📢</p><p><strong>Who This Fits 👀</strong><br />• Fresh grads / early-career 🎓<br />• Prefer people over screens<br />• Want experience without crazy pressure<br />• Okay with on-site work</p><p>Training provided, no experience needed 🌱<br />If you want something different but manageable, start with <strong>Thrive Organization</strong> 🚀</p>",
